<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ العِتْقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَهُوَ:</span> مِنْ أَفْضَلِ القُرَبِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَيُسْتَحَبُّ عِتْقُ مَنْ لَهُ كَسْبٌ، وَعَكْسُهُ بِعَكْسِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَيَصِحُّ تَعْلِيقُ العِتْقِ بِمَوْتٍ - وَهُوَ التَّدْبِيرُ -.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>